{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_11", "eventName": "淬火塵霾", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "11-16", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "榮光獵場", "storyInfo": "進入諸王長眠之所後，推進之王與阿勒黛發現了蒸汽騎士消失的真相。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"screenadapt": "showall", "image": "32_g9_kingrest", "x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些雕像......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#8$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是維多利亞的君王們。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些幻影......他們在這裡徘徊，在這裡遊蕩。"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們並非故去之人的意志，他們是......歷史與記憶的陰霾。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.5, "yScaleTo": 1.5, "duration": 50.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<color=#8f8f8f><i>“亞歷山德莉娜。”</i></color>", "x": 500.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 14.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的呼喚已經清晰可聞。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那聲音是如此地熟悉，如此地溫暖，彷彿來自她記憶中已被遺忘的角落。"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當她在花園中玩得忘了時間，有人就會帶著嗔怪與溺愛這麼呼喚她。"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<color=#9b9b9b><i>“亞歷山德莉娜。”</i></color>", "x": 50.0, "y": 150.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 16.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當她又偷偷溜出王宮大門，睜著好奇的眼睛打量一切，有人就會帶著焦急與催促這麼呼喚她。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<color=#e3e3e3><i>“亞歷山德莉娜。”</i></color>", "x": 600.0, "y": 220.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 18.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當她努力揮動木頭的小劍，在自己的幻想中所向披靡的時候，有人就會帶著欣慰與贊許這麼呼喚她。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<color=#bfbfbf><i>“亞歷山德莉娜。”</i></color>", "x": 100.0, "y": 100.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 20.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼呼喚她的人，到底是誰呢。"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯蘭王與德拉克王的塑像都陳列在這裡。", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "亞歷山德莉娜殿下，那是您的祖父，“征服高盧的”弗雷德里克三世。他的身側站著他的母親，“榮光”伊莉莎白。", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人都不由自主地放輕了腳步。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在尋找，她心裡始終清楚這份尋找不會有結果，可她的眼睛還是在忍不住搜尋著。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她停下來，仰望著一尊石像。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一尊未完成的塑像，僅僅有些大略的輪廓。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刻刀的痕跡清晰可見，華貴的長袍仍未從石料中解脫。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "視線上移，本該是面孔的地方一片模糊，只能依稀看出眉眼。"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯有頭頂的冠冕，潦草地宣示著這尊石像的身份。"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"screenadapt": "showall", "image": "32_g9_kingrest", "x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "fadetime": 0.85}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，按照規矩，這些石像都不是源石技藝製造的，它們需要耗費王室石匠很多年來雕刻打磨。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下他......離開得很突然。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下承擔了很多壓力，無論是現實中的還是法理上的。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭的債務壓得帝國喘不過氣，而已經衰微的德拉克也並不願接受阿斯蘭王室越來越長的統治。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論旁人如何評判陛下，在父親與我心中，他的一生......都絕不比在這裡的諸王遜色。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許吧，阿勒黛。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#4$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，我不記得了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許這正是他在我回憶中的模樣。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“亞歷山德莉娜。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是他在呼喚嗎？還是他們全部？"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "面前的石像們或是莊嚴，或是溫柔，面貌各不相同。"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她無法在記憶中搜尋到任何關於他們的印象，但又在心底確確實實地感受到了一種與他們的聯繫。"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有維多利亞的君王和他們的第一繼承人才有資格以維多利亞為姓氏。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此，她和他們一樣，都是維多利亞。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不再與他們對視。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起那個宏大遼闊的維多利亞，她還是更熟悉諾伯特區的小酒館，口味辛辣的粗釀麥酒，和盡力戰鬥後的酸味棒棒糖。"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她決定轉過身去。"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在視線移開的一瞬間，她就發現了雕像後的陰影。"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$2"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "警戒！", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$2"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_attack_ready", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同一時刻，所有人都握緊了自己的武器。"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，我們發現留下那些痕跡的人了。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#7$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲的屍體。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#3$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "目測超過百人。極有可能還要多得多......", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#7$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大部分屍體已經腐化分解，但從留下的裝備與服飾來看，都是薩卡茲王庭軍的精銳，還有赦罪師的衛兵。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#7$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，對於他們，連“精銳”恐怕都是一種侮辱，說實話，我沒有信心幹掉其中任何一個。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#11$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與他們作戰的是......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$2"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她感到身邊的阿勒黛呼吸粗重了起來。"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屍骸的陰影中，銅色的光芒仍然閃耀。"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連歷史也不能讓它們失色。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她繼續往前走去。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "32_i09", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 25.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帝國的騎士們從不退縮。"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個，又一個。"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刀劈，劍刺，火灼。腐蝕性的源石技藝。乾涸的血跡整個蒙住了某一具甲胄。"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "超過五米長的長釘式的投擲物，一根又一根，附著著巫術貫穿了他們的軀體。"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們依舊保持著陣型，他們依舊在作戰。"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有什麼能擊垮他們，王庭軍不能，赦罪師不能。"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死亡也不能。"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她瞬間明白過來。"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為何......過去四年間，倫蒂尼姆再也沒有響起過真正的噴氣聲。"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"screenadapt": "showall", "image": "32_g9_kingrest", "x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒸汽騎士......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "shake", "power": 3.0, "times": 1000.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.4, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛踉蹌了幾步，推進之王扶住了自己的朋友。"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還好嗎？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是空氣有點太差了，我沒事。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想到了......坎伯蘭家的那套蒸汽甲胄。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們總在捍衛，不論代價為何。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是......蒸汽騎士。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們以維多利亞的榮光為氅。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$2"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#6$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#6$2"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_battlefield_environment", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "steam"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_steamrelease", "volume": 0.1, "delay": 2.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_closeeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那些聲音在喧嘩，在嘯叫。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那是騎士們衝鋒時的噴氣聲嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那種滿溢著的，簡直要衝破一切的情感又是什麼？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她閉上眼，這些情緒讓她困惑，但結論卻一目了然。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "steam", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"screenadapt": "showall", "image": "32_g9_kingrest", "x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "推進之王", "content": "他們..."}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "推進之王", "end": "true", "content": "...被背叛了。", "joined": "他們......被背叛了。"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......背......叛？", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#10$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從殘骸的排布可以看出，在這場戰鬥中，蒸汽騎士是進攻方，而據守在這裡，阻擊他們的，是薩卡茲。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很荒誕，是不是？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡發生的，並不是蒸汽騎士在薩卡茲的圍攻之下，拼死捍衛維多利亞象徵的英雄故事。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而是......一個陷阱。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#7$2"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$2"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些榮耀的騎士們，一頭撞進了薩卡茲早就準備好的包圍網裡。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$2"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......一個建立在維多利亞諸王長眠之所的，薩卡茲包圍網。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$2"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......褻瀆！", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些薩卡茲是怎麼打開這裡的？！諸王長眠之所的鑰匙，只有......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#5$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我們親自交出去的。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......卡文迪許公爵那個叛徒！還是斯塔福德公爵那個小丑？！", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四年間再沒有蒸汽騎士出現過，就意味著......所有的蒸汽騎士都在這裡。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能把所有蒸汽騎士都調回倫蒂尼姆的，絕非一兩個被野心沖昏了頭腦的大公爵。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "背叛他們的——", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#7$2"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$dignified_intro", "key": "$dignified_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是整個維多利亞。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#6$2"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "燃燒的宮殿，金色的鬃毛。"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自從進入這裡，這些幻象總是揮之不去。"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她聽見一個男人的怒吼，她聽見藏於暗處的密謀。"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她聽見歎息，她聽見詛咒。"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "癲狂的叫喊，絕望的哀告。"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咆哮、斥責、嗚咽、惻笑。"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她聽見——"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滴答。"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是淚水滴落的聲音。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些蒸汽騎士......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "達格達努力壓抑她的哭聲。再困苦的絕境中，這位總是以騎士自稱的小姑娘也從未落淚。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而現在，大滴的淚珠正從她臉上滑落。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不明白，我不明白......為什麼......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王走上前去，輕輕抱了抱這個正在顫抖的女孩。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，達格達，我說錯了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "組成維多利亞的不僅是議會與貴族，還有你，還有我。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "仍有人願意為他們哭泣。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們沒辦法耽擱太多的時間。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但若你仍堅持稱呼我為王，那我就行使一次命令你的權力，騎士。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔樓騎士達格達，請你以騎士的禮儀......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "向他們，向這些......明知被背棄，卻仍未褪下榮光之氅的戰士。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獻上我們的敬意。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"screenadapt": "showall", "image": "32_g9_kingrest", "x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三十，三十一，三十二......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#5$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多......這麼多甲胄。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#5$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們全部死在了這裡。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的目光掠過每一具靜止的甲胄。"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "逐一行禮。"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使知道甲胄之中的人早已戰死多年，即使她手裡拿的是怪模怪樣的鋼爪而不是禮儀用的長劍，她還是一絲不苟地完成了全部禮節。"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也是騎士。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我曾經是。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和他們一樣......本來也是守衛維多利亞的騎士。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔樓騎士......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很多人都只把塔樓騎士當成一個貴族名號。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。自從陛下離我們而去，塔樓騎士就已經失去了誓言中的護衛對象。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多可笑，一群裝模作樣的騎士，守望著一座早已無人的王宮。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一個夜晚，我們佇立在塔樓之上，全都心知肚明......我們身後的王宮裡空空蕩蕩，燈火只會從面前的其他城區亮起。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小姑娘，我聽說過，你是某個大人物的繼承人。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可聽起來，塔樓騎士並不是一個多好的差事。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我的母親是曼徹斯特伯爵。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，如今我的家族所擁有的，不過是邊境城市裡一座孤零零的伯爵府而已。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的母親很愛你，她在給你謀後路。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她以為，沒有可拱衛的王的塔樓騎士是個安全的身份。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的導師也告訴我，終究會有一位國王回來，到那時，塔樓騎士必將洗清恥辱。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到薩卡茲的軍隊用兵器打碎了塔樓的大門。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲沒有對王宮動手，起碼明面上沒有，他們不想落下把柄。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，當然，他們也無法容忍塔樓騎士的存在。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們竭盡全力了。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔樓騎士的主力都已隨先王而去，只剩下幾位騎士導師......和一群自我放逐的人。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們仍然竭盡全力了！", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經蒙羞了一次，我們不能再次被羞辱！", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，以你的年紀，老獅王被吊死的時候，你還沒出生。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#2$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別給自己那麼重的擔子。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#2$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我已經宣誓加入了他們！就算沒有國王的見證封賜，我也已經是他們的一份子！", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他們騙了我，在最後的衝鋒之前，導師他們就已經決定好了，要讓我活下來。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把我送出塔樓的時候，芬恩導師已經受了很重的傷，我能看到血從他的盔甲之下洇出來。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從沒見過他露出那種表情......他說，那是解脫。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說，他的愧悔終於可以結束了，這不過是一場漫長的苟且偷生。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他為什麼不問問我的想法！我寧願和他們一起死掉！", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別覺得生命是可以輕易拋棄的東西。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死再簡單不過了，一支箭，一把刀，一次傷口感染，一小片活性化的源石，都能輕易要了你的命。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是活著很難，活下去意味著......你要與“死了就能輕鬆了”的衝動抗爭。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你走過了很長的路，認識了很好的同伴，沒有辜負信任你的長輩，這很了不起。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年長的雇傭兵輕輕地拍了拍達格達的肩膀。"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明知道對方只是個陌生人，可她卻想起了早已死去的同僚們掌心的溫度。他們的手也曾經像這樣一次次輕柔地落在她的頭頂和肩膀上。"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "逃出倫蒂尼姆這麼久，她從來沒能真正緬懷過他們。"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為戰鬥沒有結束。她不能也沒有資格回想。"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可在看到蒸汽騎士們殘缺的甲胄時，那場屬於塔樓騎士的最後的戰鬥全部回到了她的腦海中。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不理解，明明有那麼多深愛著這片土地的人，為什麼，結局總是如此？"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼英雄悄無聲息地死去，為什麼勝利的不是他們？"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她再也無法忍受。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，我幫你遮一下，你可以再偷偷哭一會。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#2$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 0.0, "duration": 4.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚......啊......", "name": "達格達"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他們周圍，甲胄沉默著。"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"screenadapt": "showall", "image": "32_g9_kingrest", "x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛，你看起來很緊張。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是嗎。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在想，你到底是怎麼看蒸汽騎士的？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們明明沒能阻止二十六年前的那件事。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不瞭解，也沒那麼關心。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#7$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我曾聽......一個叫高文的傢伙說起過，當時，並沒有蒸汽騎士在倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#7$2"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#7$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "議會調離了他們。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可等他們回來，卻仍無所作為。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#10$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，你是怎麼想的呢，阿勒黛？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$2"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能看出來，你很崇敬蒸汽騎士。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$2"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#10$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "崇敬......或許遠遠談不上。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在想，陛下在位時，冊封的最後一位蒸汽騎士是查爾斯·林奇爵士。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之後的二十多年中，卻再也沒有一位蒸汽騎士誕生。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#10$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是某種警告嗎？還是某種無人知曉的抗爭的代價？公爵們是否各自準備好了利刃，指向彼此？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許......背叛從那個時候就開始了。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#10$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無法想像......那是一場怎樣緩慢的死亡。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞殺死了它自己。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些聲音不滿地咕噥著。"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王充耳不聞，她平靜而有力地再次重複。"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由貪婪、野心與欲望拼接成的維多利亞，殺死了它自己。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，亞歷山德莉娜殿下，你會重整這一切嗎？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#6$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#4$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#4$2"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#4$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連聲音也沉默了下來，他們也在等待一個答案。"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會做好我該做的事。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}